          &lt;/tr&gt;
        &lt;/#if&gt;
      &lt;/table&gt;
    &lt;/#list&gt;

`&lt;#compress&gt;` will remove whitespace but not empty tables, but in any case the BFO renderer will automatically remove extra whitespace so it&#39;s not typically needed in NetSuite templates.

